public abstract class DefaultKeyableBeanRestQueryCollectionResource<P extends RestResource> extends KeyableBeanRestQueryCollectionResource
Base class for query-backed non-root collections of keyable beans. A non-root collection is one with a parent. This class can be extended directly.
